---------------------------------------
| -2  | client EXIT                   |
---------------------------------------
| -1  | bbs doesn't send the msg      |
---------------------------------------
| 0   | client PRINT                  |
---------------------------------------
| 30  | bbs ACCEPT "logout"           |
---------------------------------------
| 31  | bbs ACCEPT "create-chatroom"  |
|     |  ret = port, owner            |
---------------------------------------
| 32  | bbs ACCEPT "join-chatroom"    |
|     |  ret = ((addr, port), user)   |
---------------------------------------
| 33  | bbs ACCEPT "restart-chatroom" |
---------------------------------------
| 34  | bbs ACCEPT "attach"           |
---------------------------------------

RETURN_2_BBS-SERVER_SIGNAL:
------------------------
| 0  | (None)          |
------------------------
| 1  | close chatroom  |
